sub_title: Marketing & Sales expert, Student in Erasmus Universiteit Rotterdam
summary:
My name is Kirill, I come from Moscow, Russia, currently living in Rotterdam, The Netherlands. I am a Master student at the prestigious Erasmus University within the Media & Business program. I have also finished my Bachelor program within Communication and Media (IBCoM). 

I have a confident professional experience in Marketing & Sales. I worked as a Label Manager at a music agency, as a Marketing Intern at a web-development company, and as a Marketing & Sales assistant at a cosmetological resale firm. I was also collaborating with Apollo Tyres/Vredestein during the Master Consulting challenge.
